snippet.title: Ferrari Amber Essence Fragrance Review (Special Edition)
snippet.description:
Hey guys, today I am doing a rare fragrance review, this is very hard to find and was released in limited numbers for the world. comes in deluxe premium box with leather exterior. if you love woody ambery fragrances, check it out.

Amber Essence Special Edition Fragrantica link
https://www.fragrantica.com/perfume/Ferrari/Amber-Essence-34815.html

Regular Amber Essence Link

https://www.fragrantica.com/perfume/Ferrari/Amber-Essence-2016--39891.html
